# AI in Client Onboarding

## Problem
Traditional onboarding is slow and manual (e.g., KYC checks, form filling, ID verification).

## AI Applications
- ✅ OCR & NLP for parsing uploaded documents
- ✅ Identity verification via facial recognition
- ✅ Chatbots for onboarding questions
- ✅ Predictive models for onboarding drop-off risk

## Tools to Explore
- Onfido
- Trulioo
- ChatGPT + Webhooks (for Q&A bots)
